    "type": "message",
    "text": "Yeah, thats an awesome library! I have plans todo a big rewrite/refactor and will use this library as an inspiration source. I dont want to use the library myself because I want to try keep the dependencies limited and also be in control as much as possible. One thing that I do wonder:\nSvg is used here and not canvas. Performance is still very good there. Do you think svg is better performance wise for node and wire interfaces in a web interface?",
